{"tid":2229687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美智庫最新民調 6大搖擺州川普領先","createTime":"2020-10-04T14:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T04:59:54.000Z","uid":337052,"like":151,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"50d1f821e955ccc943004a97f5d2b6c001c74187","tid":2229687,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">川普確診》美智庫最新民調 6大搖擺州川普領先</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/04/3311547_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F04%2F3311547_1_1.jpg&h=fc07b458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統川普（左）與民主黨總統候選人拜登（右），將在1個月後的大選一較高下。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n2020/10/04 22:06<br />\n〔編譯孫宇青／綜合報導〕美國總統川普確診武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-9）後，競選活動被迫停擺，普遍不看好其選情。然而，<span class=\"red\">在華府和倫敦均有設點的智庫「民主研究所」（Democracy Institute），與英國「週日快報」（Sunday Express）在川普染疫後進行的最新民調顯示，川普在6大搖擺州的民調領先拜登4個百分點，最終可望拿下320張選舉人票，打敗取得218張選舉人票的拜登。</span><br />\n<br />\n據週日快報4日報導，曾成功預測英國脫歐及川普2016年當選的「民主研究所」，針對美國總統大選的最新調查結果顯示，川普的全國支持率為46％，拜登為45％，領先幅度較上月下滑2％。值得注意的是，在佛羅里達、愛荷華、密西根、明尼蘇達、賓夕法尼亞和威斯康辛等6大搖擺州，川普平均支持率達47％，領先拜登的43％，雙方差距維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n針對川普確診，68％選民表示不會影響其投票意向，且有19％稱更有可能投給川普，13％則傾向不投給他。另有3分之2選民對川普抱持同情和關懷，但也有38％認為川普慘遭報應。<br />\n<br />\n該機構指出，他們的調查對象為「有投票意願的選民」（likely voter），並非所有註冊選民。民調也詢問投票意向未定的受訪者，身邊是否有親友打算投給川普，結果77％給予正面回應。另針對川普施政，50％表示認可，48％不認可。<br />\n<br />\n儘管大法官提名、首場總統辯論會引發的爭議沸沸揚揚，但調查指幾乎沒對選情造成影響，反而有32％的美國選民認為，反種族歧視示威暴力化後的「法律和秩序」問題，是其首要考量。在經濟議題上，有7成選民認為美國經濟正在復甦，並有6成信任川普，遠勝拜登的4成。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在白人選民方面，川普和拜登的支持率分別是52％對45％；在非裔方面，僅18％支持川普，78％力挺拜登；至於西語裔方面，川普支持率為40％，拜登為50％。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3311547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3311547&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilyBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=f3fedc74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3311547&h=82956697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3311547</a>"},{"pid":"b3f08610de32a210fd6afa03076d9ffeb6f61810","tid":2229687,"uid":21545,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"陳水扁2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9139c1d7a612cae6345521f9fe60471b2cfd89db","tid":2229687,"uid":11914,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"拜登必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4594affc1f30b0d0af3ec02b9ca5093f2233f8a","tid":2229687,"uid":335434,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-R3_n8stCNvY/UJoog2wugwI/AAAAAAAAHcI/tJo-1caS810/s1600/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-R3_n8stCNvY%2FUJoog2wugwI%2FAAAAAAAAHcI%2FtJo-1caS810%2Fs1600%2F1.jpg&h=a5d4cd01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n侵侵要搖擺賓州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0bb7136464a361ec8cc811b30f5c5813a9a9d1","tid":2229687,"uid":57549,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:37:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾trump靠中國武漢肺炎贏<br />\n勝之不武<br />\n我登必勝"},{"pid":"bfd3acf62cf017dcfa472dde7c0964c7913446e6","tid":2229687,"uid":127575,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:37:37.000Z","msg":"拜登必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb